  <note>
    <para>le quantificatores avide concordara a mesura que illos pote. Per exemplo, <emphasis>a+?</emphasis> concordara le aaa in <emphasis>aaabbb</emphasis></para>
  </note>

  <table>
    <title>Regex - Quantificatores reluctante (non-avide) </title>

    <tgroup align="left" cols="2" rowsep="1">
      <colspec align="left" colnum="1"/>

